cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper deals with probabilistic relational models and inference methods, which are commonly studied in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses model conversion operators and their application to relational models, which are relevant to database systems (cs.DB). The use of joint formulas and counting conversion is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and cryptography (cs.CR), respectively.
